#### Props

There are two ways to pass props to components using MDC.

##### **Inline method**

The `{}` identifier passes props to components in a terse way by using a `key=value` syntax.

<code-group>

```mdc [index.md]
::alert{type="warning"}
The **alert** component.
::
```

```vue [Alert.vue]
